import React from 'react';
import { MDBInput, MDBRow, MDBCol } from 'mdb-react-ui-kit';



export default function CreateFlight(){
    const [planecode, setCode] = useState()
    return(
        <>
      <MDBRow className='g-1'>
        <MDBCol>
          <MDBInput id='form11Example1' label='Plane Code' value={planecode} />
        </MDBCol>
        <MDBCol>
          <MDBInput id='form11Example2' label='Departing Airport' type='email' />
        </MDBCol>
      </MDBRow>

      <hr />

      <MDBRow className='g-5'>
        <MDBCol>
          <MDBInput id='form11Example4' label='Arriving Airport' />
        </MDBCol>
        <MDBCol>
          <MDBInput id='form11Example5' label='Seats' type='number' />
        </MDBCol>
      </MDBRow>
    </>
    )
}
